	"After finishing "all bosses" TAS, I decided to improve the 
	[a class=intlink href=/1579M 
		"any% run
	]a
	", updating by 825 frames (actually ~870 frames by accounting emulation differences), by not picking a weapon, some new tricks, and better optimization. The boss battle strategy is completely different, and takes too long to finish (~1050 frames).
	$LF
]div
